N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 523.4 - Annual report

State Regulations

On or before the first of September of each
year, the Office of Court Administration shall file an annual report with the

Chief Judge reviewing the implementation of this rule and making such
recommendations as it deems appropriate. Notes
